items.title: Vietnamese singer Duc Phuc wins Russia's Intervision song contest
items.description: Vietnam was among 23 countries competing in a glitzy Russian song contest, revived three years after Russia was banned from Eurovision.

items.title: The British Army cannot keep ignoring the murder of our friend in Kenya
